p15188966.wateranalysisapp

Class Reading

  • java.lang.Object
    • p15188966.wateranalysisapp.Reading

  • class Reading
extends java.lang.Object
    An object to represent a singular Reading consisting of a Date, RGB values, User Nitrate Value, and App Calculated Nitrate Value.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      private double appNitrate

      Date, generated by app at time of reading
      private int green
      RGB values from the Image Pixel tapped by the user
      private int red
      RGB values from the Image Pixel tapped by the user
      private int userNitrate
      A nitrate value chosen by the User, engineered to be zero by default
